Help Type: command
Command: spinedigest path

Purpose:
  Find a directed path between two graph nodes in one chapter.

Usage:
  spinedigest path <archive.sdpub> <node:id> <node:id> --chapter <id>

Contract:
  - Mutates: no.
  - LLM: no.
  - JSON: no.
  - Requires graph data.

Examples:
  spinedigest path book.sdpub node:84 node:120 --chapter 3
